st naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJyFVm1v4kYQ%2Fisj1KoQEWK4EgkqPkDivOi4XpSjPVUhIos9xttb71q7axxfLv%2F9Zm3CS4D2Uwgz88zb88zyUgsxYpmwFyrEWr92dgaDwQAmmnEJVkGg2feCPuQSplnHa%2F8OudIiXHLMIW%2FPOrPu7BzqxqoUzhsudCoJYmhMlqSWKwlBTEh98CBlWgUxZ8IBtXsdaEPE9IzlrJjFWcKkeTN0gEmeMGFmRiWYx8y%2BWbprS8KsRYqeCbW2noPJogg1l4tZpILMYFhW47MgBrYpiRtgcFfYmD5HXCBQqxuzOQPrUrIwNE3QSPPhEg0oXYJpPKVOWIKUnhv63sZYNfmbgSiTQYnxBwQqSZWhUjYOFCtDJET6ipsSzVgmQyaUREhoAaIFT%2Bv5%2BssnV6oLx%2BcUA0uBSyYyBBWVCJtVtEqwERoL86yAzKVxgQa3G%2BvDVy5C6tYQmIF6OXWElMJ4wEM0jQrn2v%2FTvx9O%2FEuYF7BAiZpZbKXFGwMw5HZnYCdkbIKkTZRluZkSUol1yTUlA6S90B8aOLplKL2gaaWadqkLmFOKiCqgz00Y%2BVef732ahmaiRMiRL2JLg6TZCOU4GfOnaodCLaTSxAfoeb%2FCxS3UlabOT1V0mrCF5DYLEUafJ%2F6F68yoLP3IbRCjvGSiuEP9lwlhAC9TCTQElQq8QZFiuLZ4La%2FrEnqtrvPJUYg5UiXXtEwHUbl47crHazunQGWSqBGxwGZMjJj89ne5M%2Bf64UimkwPQJ1Bvw%2BkxuMZUvk7lItxpxNWyqtfrTCVLovfmTmWlQhlP9mLba6uNxY61tHzwaIZ5umvwnKXreWTLiVzzbGF2HLprB%2FJgQkS4V3MJ3iYzKSNXar%2BnlYNXgVSSfsgvh%2BN%2FgC1RO12kxPdfHvvb7Ap3mGd5stLqhlmBIiPxDqV9pycKZ%2B9OGKQZacZdD%2Bu4FCin4wE8uJW%2BAA0b%2BzCtjVVAbHRMg28V1aa1JuThuqU%2BJMhk%2FSAXG7R0Igm8NndBr%2FkSKx2J4jDcNhH%2BC%2BUr0QzcraaWNLcF1IefrhqHMXfo40D3IYe3n%2BAMLlZYvrQaU7pxmGkT8%2FQI7DbxjtU6oT3dVNdpjGyR4WGsHZpWWL3e%2BR7al5gOTQrUPD04CHda%2FUuzPLKYbYJXkF5vv8D%2FO6SHwfcVsspwYLTj8ZV%2FeWSE72RUghxYDhgWoVvyfSUsuKcHgekgPlLenv42wI9Od5quj3vQBjDmxrY0kvgM1st%2FjNJ2VNQrXTTh5cfzD3hubeV4bdDNmrsXagAroAfvcSXnycE3bnJz%2B2WjyT6UvwQ4DXz%2B9tCR2jlVYUiRW88mZXAe29mnsvb6Exq3BQ8%3D" id="w1_2_5_6"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#f2ccc0;strokeColor=#c96a4a;fontColor=#5a2410;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="413" y="1418" width="272" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Meat-eater problem&lt;br&gt;(saved humans eat animals)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+7]&lt;br&gt;→ Wild insects (humane pesticides)&lt;br&gt;(Michael Dickens, Vasco Grilo)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + meat_eater_problem&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The meat-eater problem: a dollar of human global health also buys decades of that person&#x27;s meat consumption, and factory farming it causes suffering the animal circle now counts. Each present-human org is charged an additive penalty — farmed-animal life-years caused per human DALY, times the suffering per factory-farmed life-year, times the animal&#x27;s welfare range. Under a heavy animal welfare range the penalty can exceed the human benefit, so saving human lives looks net-harmful. Only bites once animals count, so it requires animals_somewhat; and it is a near-term human-vs-animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 7 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJyFVm1vIkcM%2FisWalVICVkgQKDiA0nIi8r1ohztqQoRN%2Bx62enNzqxmZrOhufz3enYJ76gfohBsP7YfP%2FbkrRRgyFJhr1SApV7p7Az6%2FT6MNeMSrAJfs38X9CGTMEkbXv0cMqVF8MIxg6w%2BbUxb0%2Fa0A2VjVQKdigueSAIZGJPGieVKgh8RVg88SJhWfsSZcFD1bgPqEDI9ZRlbTKM0ZtJ8GBrAJI%2BZMFOjYswiZj8srZUlZtYiRU%2BFWlnbYNIwRM3lfBoqPzUYfJg6ECOzU%2FqhoESrmcA4r3TI%2FAjYulxugMHDwkb0OeQCgYhYm80ZWFcOCwJTBY3EHpdoQOkcTOMpdclipCzc0Pc2woKAXwyEqfRzjN%2FAV3GiDJW5dqBYGSAh0lfc5GjGMhkwoSRCTOMRNfi2Yn%2F48s2V6sLxNUHfUuALEymCCnOE9aBqOdglGguzdAGpS%2BMCDW421oOvXATUrSEwA%2BV8IggJhXGfB2gqBc7t8I%2Fh42A8vIbZAuYoUROltWTxoQ8MuN0i7ISMVZA0pbwsxykh5VjXXFMyQJoZ%2FSLC0Q1D6TmxlWias17AjFKEVAF9rsLl8Obz45DY0EzkCBnyeWSJSOJGKKfYiH8rZijUXCpNWoGu9zNc3UNZaer8VIWnMZtLbtMA4fLzeHjlOjMqTX7n1o9QXjOxeED9pwmgD28TCUSCSgTeoUgwWFm8mtdyCb1ay%2FlkKMQMqZJbGqaDKFy8euHj1Z2Tr1JJ0giZb1MmLpn8%2Flc%2BM%2