g_future_humans). || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 7 meat_eater_problem → 8 net_negative_animal_lives" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJyFVm1v4kYQ%2Fisj1KqQEmKTEhIqPuSFvOi4XpSjPVUhchZ7jLe33rV213FoLv%2B9szbvEPUDwnhmn5l55plZ3moRxiwX9lJFWOvVjo6g3%2B%2FDSDMuwSoINft3Rg%2BFhHHe9vzfoFBaRC8cCyj8oB10gpOgG5xC3ViVwWnDHR9Lgjk3Jk8zy5WEMCG0HniQMa3ChDPhwPyzNvgQMx2wgs2CJE%2BZNAtDG5jkKRMmMCrFImF2YeksLSmzFul0INTSegImj2PUXE6DWIW5wWhh6kKKzAb0oUOZVhOB6cJ2ChJtIHHKLH%2FBoIoQCHo2ZTEDFibAVhVxAwzuZzah55gLBGJrZTZHYF3GLIpMEzQSxVyiAaVLMI2HRARLkRLhht7bBCuOfjEQ5zIsMX6HUKWZMlTJyoHOyggJkV7xKjVjmYyYUBIhpR6KFjwvWzR4eXapuuP4mmFo6eALEzmCikuEVTdbJdgFGguTfAa5C%2BMOGlwvrAffuIioWkNgBupl0xAyOsZDHqFpVDg3gz8GD%2BejwRVMZjBFiZpYb2WzhYgw4naDsAMyNkFSI8u0HKeEVGJdcU3BAKmt9EWEo2uG0lNiK9PUKD2DCYWIKQN6bsLF4PrLw4DY0EyUCAXyaWKJSOJGKCfrhD9XPRRqKpWmZsOZ9zNc3kFdaar8UMWHKZtKbvMI4eLLaHDpKjMqzz5xGyYor5iY3aP%2B00TQh7exBCJBZQJvUWQYLS1ey%2Bu4gF6r43wKFGKClMkNNdNBVC6eX%2Fl4vnMKVS5JGjELbc7EBZPf%2Fyp75lyPP4h0sAf6AOo%2BHH4E1xjL97GcRhuFuFzm%2BXrtsWRpvG1uV1ZKlPF056y%2FtNpEbFhLy7FHHBbZpsFzlo7nka0gcU3yqdlw6CwdyIMJEeNOziW4T2aajEKp3ZrmDl4FUo30Y3F1Pvwb2AtqNxcZ6f2np966uqIN5Vmezmd1paxQkZF0h9JuzRMdZ1sbELKcZsZtD%2Bu0FCo3x314dC19AyIbezCuDVVIanRKg%2B%2BV1Ma1JhTRsqSe22OyvleLDWo6iQR%2BhfphWXfH77a7DXhvbga5oc1WzZWY7YdfF8YWavvMa5%2F4%2B0G%2FkQrB3QRUseZ2BvXzz9eN%2FSE21OViLCL4x8enp7v453ef4Qgu58ADaTVmtA8x1ybh2Qcx1kW6VUfX63Y6x7txRtTi22qxDZFNc9wPvaFwB%2B23zugq2Ub7mtCOyoCIoasO4V6rf4j2D3q6PhtVtu3u2Q7k%2F%2B3g%2FeC7w1VF8Du7TA%2BH14OrDxjdmsASZE%2BvwLAYnQAeqpmEB7pLmA6TD9LbGd0V8JMbWU2Ly92FfRhyY1saaW4N1ssfRml7MatXI9WEtx%2BvP%2BC1tRbjvUHrbuIutz7MgR69p%2FkmGO29Hke3d19X49yD8j8IJ8InizuSFgWnLAwN89qNSxGcx3r0say9%2FweBASbt" id="w1_2_5_6_7_8"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#e9b0a0;strokeColor=#b8402a;fontColor=#511810;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="455" y="1896" width="272" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><ob