y: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 6 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx9lW1v4jgQx7%2FKCN3poKI0oUtXy4kXUOiDjr2tutytTqWiJpkQ3zp2ZDukuW6%2F%2B44TykOBe9WUGf%2Fm6T%2F2Sy3EiGXCXqoQa93a2Rn0ej2YaMYlWAWBZv8V9JFLmGZtz%2F8AudIiXHLMIfdn7dkF1I1VKVw03MGpJEDfmCxJLVcSgpg4XfAgZVoFMWfCYfxPbfAhYnrGclbM4ixh0rwZ2sAkT5gwM6MSzGNm3ywXYLIoQs3lYhapIDMYlvFGLIiBbYJyAwzuChvTd8QFApWyMZszsA7KwtA0QSPVzyUaULqEaTylXFmClgIZ%2Bt3GWJXxm4Eok0HJ%2BB0ClaTKUCobBzorQyQi%2FcRNSTOWyZAJJRESarBowdO6f6Plk0vVHcfnFANLB5dMZAgqKgmbVrdK2ACNhXlWQObCuIMGtwvrwoRYN66bCGNkiwyrg9ejP0f3%2FcloCPMCFihRM4uttHgbKYbc7nTohIxNkMpWebgmEqlkDbmmVAFpEPSHOoyu%2B0ovqD2ppsHpAuYUIuIBp%2B8mDEZXX%2B5HVL5moiTkyBexpc5RM4RyIov5UzU0oRZSaRo%2BfPJ%2BhctbqCtNpZ6q6DRhC8ltFiIMvkxGlw3Kx6gs%2FYPbIEY5ZKK4Q%2F2XCaEHL1MJkKJKBd6gSDFcW7yW13EBvVbH%2BeQoxBwpk2uankNULp5f%2BXi%2BcwpUJkkLEQtsxsSAye9%2Fl0NyrudHIp0cQJ9A3YfTY7jGVL5O5SLcKcTlssrXa08lS6L35nZlpUQZT%2FbO%2BmurjcWOtbSce9TDPN01eM7S8Tyy5VyE82xhdhw6awfyYEJEuJdzCffJTKuQK7Vf08rBqyDVDj%2Fkw%2F74H2BL1G4RUhL4L4%2FdbXWFO8qzPFkt50ZZgSIj6Q6lfbdAdJy9u5UgzaxxAubWaSlQbnF78OBG%2BgLUbOzCtDZWAanRKQ2%2BV1Kb1pqQh%2BuSupAgk%2FWDWmzQ0Ekk8NrchV7zJVZ7JIrDuG0h%2FB%2FlG8kM3PVLJWluC6j3P181DjN35OOg%2B8j%2B7Wc4g8sVayStxpQuNcy0iXl6BLstvGO57l1Mh1k7Mq1Yfsf%2FeP5hD%2Fg1prsmBaqfnhGEO63%2BpXYemc22xkvqHu4bSZ2eCUMMA%2FW4yjSl%2B5bUFKI50tH9BTlM74%2FHV6Phkfa9W6EjhFswLEI34PtqqeCebn%2Bmg%2FhIbnu7twE%2Fup3TdPO416sHY25sSyMtnsF6%2BY9R2g6KerUTTXj58fwDnltbMV4bdF%2FN3XPUgxXowXtcrfLk4IM2ubn9utnHLpQPO6duz99eNdp0TlkY2satN5IiOI%2Ft6FNZe%2F0Jo%2BnzWA%3D%3D" id="w1_2_6"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#f2ccc0;strokeColor=#c96a4a;fontColor=#5a2410;" vertex="1" parent