y (AMF)&lt;br&gt;(Frank Ramsey, Tyler Cowen)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + future_humans_matter_with_discounting&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Future people are inside the circle, but with a positive pure-time discount rate — the moderate longtermist position. A modest discount is enough to keep present, measurable global health competitive with future-protecting work; remove it (the next assumption) and the astronomical numbers take over. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1VW1z4jYQ%2Fis7TDslGULs0Hw4OnyA4LzMcb1MjvamEzJE2Gusnix5JBnHzeW%2Fd2UTXoL5hNGunn17Hu1rK8KY5cJeqQhb%2Fdb5OQwGA5hqxiVYBaFm%2F5X0UUiY5Ree%2FzsUSotoxbGAwp%2F3oG2syqB34q7NJF0fGpOnmeVKQpgQSh88yJhWYcKZcCD%2BpwvwIWZ6zgpWzpM8ZdK8G3oQ5zbXuD6ep8xa1POC22QecROqXFoul1WkgIUJsG04boDBfWkT%2Bo65QKAStmZzDjZhFlgUmQ5opLq5RANKV2AazyhLliKF44bObYJ1Ab8ZykmGFcYfEKo0U4ZS2DrQXRkhIdIRNxWasUxGTCiJkFJjRReeN30LVs8uVXcdXzIMLV1cMZEjqLhC2La4W4GN0FhY5CXkLoy7aHC3sD7c8BV%2BRyHAzYJy0tyW0B5%2BuT6pEW6CP4OH4TQYw6KEJUrUzGI3K99nihG3e606JWMHpLJ1Qq6bhFRhjbmmnAHj2P1Qq9GNQekl9SnTPGW6hAWFiHnI6bsDo%2BD660NAfdBMVAgF8mXipkhdEcqxLOHP9fSEWkqlUyLKJ%2B9XuLqDttJU85mKz1K2lNzmEcLo6zS4cpUZlWefuQ0TlGMmynvUf5kIBvA6kwAZqkzgLYoMo43F63qXLqDXvXQ%2BBfVsgZTJDY3RQdQunl%2F7eL5zqjiHOmahzZkYMfnj72pazrV3JNJpA%2FQptH04OwZ3MpNvM7mM9gpxuazz9S5mkqXxR%2FNFbaVEGU8P7vobq03EnrWy9DzqYZHtGzxnufQ8shVcRIt8afYcLjcO5MGEiPEg5wrcJzNpolDqsKa1g1eD1GJ%2BLMbDyT%2FAVqidIjJi%2Bi9P%2FV12RXvMszxdq3TLrFCRkXiH0n5QEl1nHx4myHJrHIG5dVwKlVPwAB7dSF%2BBmo19mLUmKiQ2OqbBj5pqs1YHimhTUh9SZLLdyMUTGroPb519SKfWWkWibAbbpcFxjGbFNyPuUacZcnj3Bc7hao0VSKsxo5cNc20Snh2B3SVdM%2ByUJnTrHnOECbJljs1IewR1SN4B0reEnpcMqGxaHgj3Wv1LPTwyjl1aN8N9J3bTijCEYaCd1Clm9NYSgSI0Rxp5qIlm9OFkch2Mj3Ttg2oqBCebw5GAYTG60T7UUoIHevyZDpMj6R0obpvdk1OapvfGLa8BTLixXY0kN4Pt6o9R2o7Kdq2EDrz%2BfPkJL92dGG8n9Eot3DYawBro0XtaC3jauM%2Bmt3fftirsQ%2BFWMKeGL96XGumbUxaGNLizIimC89iNPpOtt%2F8BVmrzRg%3D%3D" id="w1_3"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#f2e3b3;strokeColor=#c9a72a;fontColor=#57450e;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1076" y="701" width="229" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="No pure-time discount&lt;br&gt;(astronomical stakes)&lt;br&gt;[1+3+4]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;(Toby Ord, Nick Bostrom)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Accept that future people count exactly as much as present ones (Ord, MacAskill) and Bostrom&#x27;s astronomical-waste argument follows: the expected size of the future dwarfs the present, and reducing existential risk dominates everything measurable. This is the stop Ajeya Cotra&#x27;s near-termist deliberately gets off before. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1VW1z4jgM%2Fisa5nYOOpQmffmw3PABWvoyx952uuzt3JQONYlCfOvYGdshzXX7309OKJASPhEs%2BfEj6ZH02goxYpmwlyrEVr91cgKDwQCmmnEJVkGg2X8FfeQSZtmp559DrrQIVxxzyP352fwc2saqFM477uJMEsDQmCxJLVcSgphw%2BuBByrQKYs6Eg%2FE%2Fn4IPEdNzlrNiHmcJk%2BbdcAZRZjON6%2BN5wqxFPc%2B5jechN4HKpOVy%2Be5%2BDlLtns9rt0s%2BYxbEwLakuAEG94WN6TviAoFC3ZrNCdiYWWBhaLqgkfLDJRpQugTTeEyxsASJFDd0bmOswvzdEHMZlBh%2FQKCSVBlHdONAd2WIhEhHvKJmLJMhE0oiJFQA0YPnTX7Hq2dH1V3HlxQDSxdXTGQIKioRtqXolWAjNBYWWQGZe8ZdNLgbWB%2BGd2BYhLaA9gOGuVIhPJAT00HcqTBuxn%2BNH4bT8RUsCliiRM0s9tLivfoYcltL1hEZu1QDW1Fy%2BSSkEuuKa2INGEXuh5KNrhBKLylTqeYJ0wUs6ImIB5y%2BuzAaX399GFMmNBMlQo58GbuqUl6EcnqM%2BXNVP6GWUumEBPXZ%2BwSXd9BWmqI%2BVtFxwpaS2yxEGH2dji9dZEZl6Z%2FcBjHKKyaKe9TfTQgDeJ1JgBRVKvAWRYrhxuL1vAv3oNe7cD45CrFAYnJDhXQQlYvnVz6e75xKDaKOWGAzJkZM%2Fvy7rJdzPTvw0lED9BG0fTg%2BBNeZybeZXIa1QByXNV%2FvdCZZEn00n1ZWIsp4snfX31htLGrW0nLmUQ7ztG7wnOXC88iWcxEusqWpOVxsHMiDCRHhHucS3CezruTYzMv3vAqkaufH%2FGo4%2BQfYCrXriZS0%2FttTf1ddYU15lifrPt0qK1BkJN2htB96ia6zDwMM0swaJ2BunZYC5Xp