ou are more likely a momentary Boltzmann brain than a person with a past and a future, the only thing that registers is whatever you happen to feel right now. Every charity collapses to the same low pleasant-thought level of value; the ranking goes flat and no donation beats any other. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 9 living_in_simulation → 11 boltzmann_brain" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJydVW1v2zgM%2FitEsOHSIkntvgxoDvmQtukLlt2KLnfDoS5cxaZj3WTJkOS4Xtf%2FfpSd13YDLvcpjkg%2BIh8%2BpJ5bMSasEPZcxdjqtw4OYDAYwEQzLsEqiDT7XtFHKSEoDj3%2FGEqlRTznWELph0fhcXga%2Bj60jVU5%2BP6eCw8kwQyNKbLcciUhSgmtDx7kTKso5Uw4MP%2F0EHxImA5ZyaowLTImzdJwBElhC42L4zBj1qIOS27TMOYmUoW0XM6W7scg1eZ5uBW99DoFwefOymVoeFYIVqe3zMWHqRL2O0XIcOoIqOsYsSgFti6GG2BwW9mUvhMuEIiotdkcgE2ZBRbHpgMaiV0u0YDSNZjGLnHAMqRiuKFzm2JDz2%2BGKpZRjfE7RCrLlXEFrhwoVsZIiHTETY1mLJMxE0oiZNQ%2B0YPHVXdG80eXqgvHpxwjS4FzJgoEldQI60b2arAzNBamRQWFu8YFGtwsrE8UU1zDuROCZvKb%2B5sQjQ3E1eiP0d1wMrqAaQUzlKiZxV5eLSMw5naLq30ydhxuk5Gjk5ACuerDGOcoYAA%2Bdj8A0BWu1kQg1s3PBTLDpItWxSy1HdeL8mI4%2FvvgXdB074Jrqh0wSdwPtQxdO5WeEd%2B55hnTFUwp04RHnL47cDa6%2FHw3Ij41EzVCiZyg6TpiVyg3Eyl%2FbFQg1EwqnZGcT733cH4DbaWJu65KuhmbSW6LGOHs82R0vkdlGVXkH7mNUpQXTFS3qP80MdX2HEiAHBVVc40ix3hl8XreibvQ6504nxKFmCJlckVycBCNi%2Bc3Pp7vnOoJQJ2wyBZMnFGP%2Fqq77lyPfnHT%2Fk%2Bg96HtQ%2FdXcHuBfAnkLN4qxOWyyNc7DCTLktfmw8ZKiTKevYn1V1abii1rbTnyiMMy3zZ4znLieWQruYinxcxsOZysHMiDCZHgm5xrcJ%2FMNFulUm9rWjh4DUizFO5rmQGbo3aTldPEvHvob6or3lKe5dli2tfKihQZSXco7auJpHD2an1CXljjBMzdsNGic5tgAPeupc9AZGMfgtZYRaRGpzT41kgtaHWgjFcl9eHVbL10thGu%2BByboRHV%2F4n9SkoC9xZQ1prbCtrDT5d7uyINbz7BAZwvIEbSasxp%2F2GhTcrzXdEmRPu1ewkQxshmBe4K8CWlVZED1UbPFcKtVv8QQbuifCWB0oYyFGqgnTYJ5bR2SQMxmt1JGo8vRxe7UwuGJeg6c9cIHu5o1TMdpf8pgwc3AsvdP4AxN7anyaoNtus%2FRml7VrUbiXbg%2BcfTD3jqbcC%2B7NH6mLrnZrB8RO69h8VkTX76YE2ub76sx6MPpXtjOdE4Xb5aNHicsjA0HBtvIN3gPDZvD2Tr5V%2BGxBYi" id="w1_3_4_9_11"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;font